episodes.title: Ep. 113: The Screamers
episodes.description: From psychological thrillers to Donegal's unique 70s/80s cult history as well as the viral bestselling lipstick that suits everyone - we're covering a multitude this week! We also discuss how Irish childhood runner (trainer) shaming has changed/evolved through the years.
